{% extends "email/base.twig" %}
{% block content %}
    <p>Hi {{ name }},</p>
    <p>It’s been a while since you were an active member of Vlaamse Jeugdherbergen (Youth Hostels in Flanders). But we haven’t forgotten you! In the meantime, a lot has changed: Our name changed to Hi Flanders, we launched a  <a href="https://www.hiflanders.be/nl/home"><strong>brand-new website,</strong></a> and we’ve gone fully digital.</p>
    <p>Good news: there's still a place for you on this journey! If you renew your membership now, you’ll instantly receive 10% off your next booking—both in Belgium and abroad.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 30px"><strong>What do you need to do? </strong> Simple! Click the button below and renew your membership online in just a few clicks:</p>
    <a style="color: #102438;" class="button" href="{{ activationUrl }}">I renew my membership</a>
    <p style="margin-top: 40px">Your renewed membership gives you access to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Exclusive discounts and inspiration for stays at Hi Flanders and Hostelling International</li>
        <li>No more paperwork or membership card - everything is digital and easy to access</li>
        <li>Worried about spam? No need! You stay in control and decide how often you hear from us. Plus, we handle your data securely and confidentially in compliance with privacy laws. Check our privacy policy for more info.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>How much does it cost?</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>30 years old or younger? Your membership is free!</li>
        <li>31 and up? Just €10 per year—which you’ll easily earn back with 10% off all your bookings.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Need help?</strong></p>
    <p>If you have any questions or trouble activating your membership, feel free to contact us at  <a style="color: #fac000;" href="mailto:hi@hiflanders.be">hi@hiflanders.be</a> or call <a style="color: #fac000;" href="tel:+3232327218">+32 3 232 72 18</a> during office hours. We’re happy to assist!</p>
    <p>We hope to welcome you soon in one of our hostels!</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px">Warm regards,</p>
    <p>The Hi Flanders Team</p>
{% endblock %}